        requests_i_j_k_l_s_l0(i, j, k, l, l0, s) of  number # Запрашиваемый объем НП
        requests_i_j_k_l_l0(i, j, k, l, l0)      of  number
        requests_i_j_k_l_s_l0 of matrix(Product, Refinery, Region, Market_participant, Queue, Ship_terms)
        requests_i_j_k_l_l0   of matrix(Product, Refinery, Region, Market_participant, Queue)
            where
